 He's arrived! He's here! 

191
00:21:28,670 --> 00:21:31,620
 Ji Eun Ho! Ji Eun Ho! 

192
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:34,920
  Just a moment. Just a word! Just one statement! Can you open your window? 

