216
00:23:36,730 --> 00:23:41,620
Remember last time I told you about President Hwang, that guy who left behind his entire mess for Eun Ho to deal with.

217
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:44,980
 I swear, if we ever catch him... 

218
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:05,730
 Hello? 

219
00:24:05,730 --> 00:24:07,200
Oppa.

220
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,900
 Yeah. 

